item.description: I’m a software engineer in Frederick Maryland. Currently learning as much as possible and blogging about it here! As a career, I work as a full stack web developer at iHire. We primarily work with Microsoft’y technologies. Here is our Stackshare page if you are interested in that sort of thing. For fun and profit, I’m diving into the world of software development where I’m learning about Python, statistics, machine learning, application architechure and more!
